
This repo contain a compiled version of:

AstroVim - NVim
https://github.com/AstroNvim/AstroNvim

Verible - The last working version for CentOS 6
https://github.com/chipsalliance/verible

RipGrep - To use with AstroVim Telescope
https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep

Git 2.9.5 - Newer than the 1.7 version on CentOS 6, also to use with GitSigns in AstroVim
https://git-scm.com/

Changes:
- Add Verible format command to Keymap
SPC + v + f
- Add fullpath file name to bufferline via Feline
- Turn off relative number by default

Usage:

1. Check what shell you are using and use the corresponding install script
2. Run the script
source bash_install.sh
OR
source csh_install.csh

Useful keymap:

AstroNVim will show hint if you pause during your inputs

1. Basic keymaps

|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
|           Action           | Keymap  (SPC means SPACE) |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Open recent files          |        SPC + f + o        |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Find files by name         |        SPC + f + f        |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Find words (Live grep)     |        SPC + f + w        |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Find word under cursor     |        SPC + f + c        |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Find buffer (Opened files) |        SPC + f + b        |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Scroll up preview          |          Ctrl + u         |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Scroll down preview        |          Ctrl + d         |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Search keymap              |        SPC + s + k        |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Search help                |        SPC + s + h        |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Format SystemVerilog code  |        SPC + v + f        |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Toggle code comment        |          SPC + /          |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Open floating terminal     |          Ctrl + \         |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Toggle file explorer       |          SPC + e          |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|
| Focus file explorer        |          SPC + o          |
|:--------------------------:|:-------------------------:|

2. When in File Explorer

|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
|          Action         |   Keymap  |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Show help (all keymaps) |     ?     |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Show hidden files       |     H     |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Add file                |     a     |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Add directory           |     A     |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Rename file             |     r     |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Fuzzy finder            |     /     |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Navigate                | Arrow key |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Open file               |   Enter   |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Copy                    |     c     |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Move                    |     m     |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|
| Toggle preview          |     P     |
|:-----------------------:|:---------:|

